ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would definitely recommend this class to another student.
Excellent second course in the IR sequence that focuses on research design rather than building baseline knowledge of IR theory etc.
I strongly recommend this class. Though the class is pretty intense, you can learn a lot, and after taking this class, you will have a good sense of what IR is about.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was helpful to take a look at the "new IR;" that certainly informed my work.
It's helped me focus on research that I care about and hope to extend with my dissertation.
